{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3048210/extras/Wishlist_Eng.gif?t=1737477985\" />Imagine inheriting a farm AND a shop. What would you do with it?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Yes, it's a mess. Yes, it needs work. But it's yours\u2014and it\u2019s free. In this economy?!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3048210/extras/SmallGif4.gif?t=1737477985\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Restore Your Farm</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Transform this abandoned land into the thriving farm it deserves to be.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Grow your own crops, take care of animals (coming soon), and upgrade your surroundings.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">It'll take effort, but soon you'll be able to acquire new tools, improve your buildings, and customize the farm of your dreams.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3048210/extras/SmallGif3.gif?t=1737477985\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Open Your Own Shop</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Why sell your crops and produce to someone else when you can do it yourself?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Ever heard of a farmer's market? Well, this shop has the &quot;farmer&quot; part sorted.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Organize your shop, manage the goods on your shelves, and handle all the finances!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Sell directly to customers, or hire some help\u2014you\u2019re only human, after all.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3048210/extras/SmallGif2.gif?t=1737477985\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Master the Art of Multitasking</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Running a farm and a shop at the same time isn\u2019t easy. But you\u2019ve got this!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Balance your time between tending to crops, serving customers, and managing the chaos.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Do it all yourself, or hire help and order goods that you don't produce (at least, not yet).</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Will you focus on strict business? Go personal and sustainable? Maybe a bit of both? Only you can decide.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3048210/extras/SmallGif1.gif?t=1737477985\" /></p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3048210/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1737477985","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3048210/page.bg.jpg?t=1737477985","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3048210/2ab9e61ad54062a59ecc318e10e646308f465c25/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1737477985","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3048210/2ab9e61ad54062a59ecc318e10e646308f465c25/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1737477985","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[],"notes":null},"detailed_description":"<h1>ADD THE FULL GAME TO YOUR WISHLIST</h1><p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3048210/extras/Wishlist_Eng.gif?t=1737477985\" />Imagine inheriting a farm AND a shop. What would you do with it?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Yes, it's a mess. Yes, it needs work. But it's yours\u2014and it\u2019s free. In this economy?!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3048210/extras/SmallGif4.gif?t=1737477985\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Restore Your Farm</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Transform this abandoned land into the thriving farm it deserves to be.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Grow your own crops, take care of animals (coming soon), and upgrade your surroundings.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">It'll take effort, but soon you'll be able to acquire new tools, improve your buildings, and customize the farm of your dreams.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3048210/extras/SmallGif3.gif?t=1737477985\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Open Your Own Shop</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Why sell your crops and produce to someone else when you can do it yourself?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Ever heard of a farmer's market? Well, this shop has the &quot;farmer&quot; part sorted.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Organize your shop, manage the goods on your shelves, and handle all the finances!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Sell directly to customers, or hire some help\u2014you\u2019re only human, after all.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3048210/extras/SmallGif2.gif?t=1737477985\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Master the Art of Multitasking</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Running a farm and a shop at the same time isn\u2019t easy. But you\u2019ve got this!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Balance your time between tending to crops, serving customers, and managing the chaos.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Do it all yourself, or hire help and order goods that you don't produce (at least, not yet).</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Will you focus on strict business? Go personal and sustainable? Maybe a bit of both? Only you can decide.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3048210/extras/SmallGif1.gif?t=1737477985\" /></p>","developers":["SleepySealsGames"],"genres":[{"description":"Simulation","id":"28"},{"description":"Free To Play","id":"37"}],"header_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_i